### Summary of ASX Announcement (ANG) – Board & Executive Management Update  

- **CEO Transition**: Sybrandt Van Dyk appointed as new CEO/MD, replacing David Singleton (remaining as Non-Executive Director).  
- **New Non-Executive Director**: Ian Stone appointed, replacing Chris Indermaur as Audit & Risk Committee Chair.  

*No material financial, capital, or operational impacts identified.*
